---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout title="About — Clemente Lacerda" description="About Clemente Lacerda — background, beliefs, and principles.">
  <section class="about-page">
    <h1>About</h1>
    <div class="about-content">
      <p>
        I am the oldest of three siblings. I am passionate about learning, building, and craft.<sup>1</sup> I also believe that sharing the journey with people you admire, respect, and love makes any project and experience better.
      </p>
      <p>
        I was born and raised in Brazil. I lived in Singapore while completing my Master's in Finance at NUS Business School, and I am now based in New York as a first-year MBA student at Columbia. Singapore expanded my self-awareness, challenged old beliefs, and reshaped my worldview. New York reinforced how much a city can shape your inner life. Environment, context, and people matter.
      </p>
      <p>
        I believe that everything you do matters. Integrity is non-negotiable. There is no cheating reality. Compounding may be the closest thing we have to magic.<sup>2</sup> Small actions, repeated consistently over long periods, create outsized outcomes.<sup>3</sup>
      </p>
      <p>
        I keep a small set of principles and a long list of curiosities.
      </p>
    </div>
    <footer class="footnotes">
      <p><span class="footnote-marker">1</span> There is long-term satisfaction to be found not in attaining, but in becoming. Craftsmanship carries through a product and service — it has weight, it has meaning. <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8VHOO_WvOf4" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Inside Mizuno: Craft, Patience & Mastery</a></p>
      <p><span class="footnote-marker">2</span> Often attributed to Albert Einstein: "Compound interest is the eighth wonder of the world."</p>
      <p><span class="footnote-marker">3</span> Popularized through "the butterfly effect," the idea that small changes can produce large consequences in complex systems.</p>
    </footer>
  </section>
</PageLayout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    padding-top: var(--space-3xl);
  }

  .about-page h1 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .about-content {
    max-width: var(--content-max-width);
  }

  .about-content p {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: var(--leading-body);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-body);
  }

  .about-content p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .about-content sup {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 0;
    vertical-align: super;
  }

  .footnotes {
    max-width: var(--content-max-width);
    margin-top: var(--space-3xl);
    padding-top: var(--space-lg);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .footnotes p {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: var(--leading-body);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .footnotes p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .footnote-marker {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .footnotes a {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .footnotes a:hover {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .about-page {
      padding-top: var(--space-4xl);
    }
  }
</style>
